"><p>Vi følger landskampene:</p><h3>Ute av VM-kvalifiseringen etter nytt sjokktap</h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/vi-foelger-15/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Innsikt</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 13.okt. 22:58</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-alexis_mac_allister card-type-nyhet card-author-stefan-fosse" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/pemj0cz3/gettyimages-2240352386_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0.11336519192230615,0.20570688618600563,0.09736395868660398,0.12833556860750128&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c6ace3ce710&amp;cdv=638959750338570000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/pemj0cz3/gettyimages-2240352386_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0.11336519192230615,0.20570688618600563,0.09736395868660398,0.12833556860750128&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c6ace3ce710&amp;cdv=638959750338570000" title="GettyImages-2240352386_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2240352386_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Det kommer gode nyheter fra USA – eller gjør det?</h3><p class="card-text">Alexis Mac Allister ligger en til å starte treningskampen mot Puerto Rico natt til onsdag.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/kommer-gode-nyheter-45/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 13.okt. 21:35</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-david_lynch tag-kommentar card-type-kommentar card-author-david-lynch" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2ozaaidr/17_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c6fda997a00&amp;cdv=638959772020800000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2ozaaidr/17_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c6fda997a00&amp;cdv=638959772020800000" title="- (17)_16x9.png" alt="- (17)_16x9.png" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Nå kommer perioden som vil «avgjøre» sesongen</h3><p class="card-text">David Lynch skriver i ukens kommentar at Liverpools skrantende form kanskje har blitt skrevet og snakket litt for mye om.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/naa-kommer-perioden-3e/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Kommentar</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 13.okt. 18:31</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Complete"><div class="bg-red has-bg"><div class="content-complete complete-meny"><div clas="complete-content-data"><div class="row"><div class="listBlock "><div class="nocustomsettings" ><div class="Menu-list overflow-hidden horizontal-scrollable"><ul class="nav nav-pills itms-10  row row-cols-2  gy-3 gx-3"><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/lfc/">Artikler</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/statistikk/tabell/">Tabell</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/kamper/2025/">Terminliste</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/spillere/spillerstall/">Spillerstall</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="/statistikk/2025/">Statistikk</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="http://www.kopshop.no/">KopShop</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link " href="https://kopforum.liverpool.no/">KopForum</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-ryan_gravenberch tag-wataru_endo tag-skader card-type-nyhet card-author-stefan-fosse" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/jkeha1zr/gettyimages-2240298440_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0.1784379911876111,0,0.16192120384446906,0.4434997681249034&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c62f92cda00&amp;cdv=638959716699200000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/jkeha1zr/gettyimages-2240298440_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0.1784379911876111,0,0.16192120384446906,0.4434997681249034&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c62f92cda00&amp;cdv=638959716699200000" title="GettyImages-2240298440_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2240298440_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Dysser ned Koemans skadekommentar</h3><p class="card-text">Ryan Gravenberch forlot banen til pause da Nederland slo Finland komfortabelt søndag kveld.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/dysser-ned-koemans-1e/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 13.okt. 17:00</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-liverpool_fc_women card-type-women card-author-jens-bessesen" data-category="women"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/tcrmafsq/gettyimages-2240626051_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c3f3cb6ee60&amp;cdv=638959563213500000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/tcrmafsq/gettyimages-2240626051_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c3f3cb6ee60&amp;cdv=638959563213500000" title="GettyImages-2240626051_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2240626051_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Har fått sin verste start noensinne</h3><p class="card-text">Fem tap på fem kamper er fasit etter en rotete sommer for Liverpool FC Women. </p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/faatt-verste-start-31/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Women</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 13.okt. 15:21</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Complete"><div class="bg-pink has-bg"><div class="content-complete complete-pausepraten"><div clas="complete-content-data"><div class="row"><div class="listBlock "><div class="pt-3 px-3" ><h2 class="section-heading pb-3"><i class="me-2 bi bi-pause"></i>Ukens Pausepraten</h2><div class="Card-list overflow-hidden horizontal-scrollable"><div class="has-category itms-200  row row-cols-3  gt-3 gx-3"><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-pausepraten tag-reise card-has-embeded card-type-pausepraten card-author-redaksjonen" data-category="pausepraten"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/rbchmeny/nyberynnger-ss_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3a1740beb0d0&amp;cdv=638957192459170000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/rbchmeny/nyberynnger-ss_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3a1740beb0d0&amp;cdv=638957192459170000" title="nyberynnger ss_16x9.jpg" alt="nyberynnger ss_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Liverpoolreise for nybegynneren</h3><p class="card-text">Skal du på din første Liverpool-tur? Vi har noen tips til deg.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/liverpoolreise-23/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-pausepraten card-has-embeded card-type-pausepraten card-author-redaksjonen" data-category="pausepraten"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/icibfut2/pausepraten-ss07101_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3845502fa1b0&amp;cdv=638955191263470000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/icibfut2/pausepraten-ss07101_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3845502fa1b0&amp;cdv=638955191263470000" title="pausepraten ss07101_16x9.jpg" alt="pausepraten ss07101_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">– Slot må ikke vike fra planen sin nå</h3><p class="card-text">Vi tar en prat om tingenes tilstand i Liverpool, etter tre tap på rad.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/slot-maa-ikke-vike-20/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-pausepraten tag-champions_league tag-ibrahima_konate tag-arne_slot tag-galatasaray card-has-embeded card-type-pausepraten card-author-arve-vassbotten" data-category="pausepraten"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/cenbimuj/30092025-pausepraten-galatasaray-yt_16x9.jpeg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3276e1c8b870&amp;cdv=638948807089830000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/cenbimuj/30092025-pausepraten-galatasaray-yt_16x9.jpeg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3276e1c8b870&amp;cdv=638948807089830000" title="30092025 Pausepraten Galatasaray YT_16x9.jpeg" alt="30092025 Pausepraten Galatasaray YT_16x9.jpeg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">– Det henger ikke sammen, og Konate er en katastrofe</h3><p class="card-text">Frustrasjonen er stor etter tapet i Champions League.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/henger-ikke-sammen-7/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-pausepraten card-has-embeded card-type-pausepraten card-author-redaksjonen" data-category="pausepraten"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/cu0hsgi3/ppss2909_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3165b7041bf0&amp;cdv=638947633846230000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/cu0hsgi3/ppss2909_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3165b7041bf0&amp;cdv=638947633846230000" title="ppss2909_16x9.jpg" alt="ppss2909_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">– Han ser ikke ut som seg selv, og det skremmer meg litt </h3><p class="card-text">Så Liverpool var ikke uslåelige likevel.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/9/ser-ikke-ut-seg-selv-45/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="embededBlock "><div class="rounded fg-black pb-3 pe-3" ><div class="text-end"><span>Følg oss</span><a target="_blank" href="https://podcasts.apple.com/no/podcast/liverpool-no-pausepraten/id1431864965"><i class="mx-1 bi bi-apple"></i>Apple</a><a target="_blank" href="https://open.spotify.com/show/3HLpnzLaYwFUgB8ZEu4Miw?si=231c520550f54330"><i class="mx-1 bi bi-spotify"></i>Spotify</a><a target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/@lfcscn"><i class="mx-1 bi bi-youtube"></i>Youtube</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-NoImage"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100"><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><p><strong>Brentford - Liverpool 25.10:&nbsp;</strong></p><h3>Kom på Pausepraten spesial med David Lynch </h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/9/pausepraten-spesial-44/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Supporterklubben</span><abbr>/ 11.sep. 9:48</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-alexander_isak tag-landslag card-type-liveblogg card-author-stefan-fosse" data-category="liveblogg"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/k0xg4dic/18_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c7d38c22b60&amp;cdv=638959829435100000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/k0xg4dic/18_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c7d38c22b60&amp;cdv=638959829435100000" title="- (18)_16x9.png" alt="- (18)_16x9.png" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Starter på topp i skjebnekamp for Sverige</h3><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/starter-topp-2f/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Liveblogg</span><abbr>/ 13.okt. 20:14</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-wataru_endo tag-skader card-type-nyhet card-author-jens-bessesen" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/kkgf4hha/gettyimages-2237690453_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.378,0.21584497271297753&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c3c90d7ac30&amp;cdv=638959551740030000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/kkgf4hha/gettyimages-2237690453_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.378,0.21584497271297753&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c3c90d7ac30&amp;cdv=638959551740030000" title="GettyImages-2237690453_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2237690453_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Trolig ikke alvorlig skade for Endo</h3><p class="card-text">Landslagstreneren lot Liverpool-spilleren hvile. </p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/trolig-ikke-alvorlig-51/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 13.okt. 13:55</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Complete"><div class="bg-white has-bg"><div class="content-complete complete-fcquiz"><div clas="complete-content-data"><div class="row"><div class="embededBlock "><div class="nocustomsettings" ><iframe src="https://fcquiz.app/no/embed/club-league/1165" width="100%" height="550" frameborder="0"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Complete"><div class="bg-red has-bg"><div class="content-complete complete-kopshop"><div clas="complete-content-data"><div class="row"><div class="listBlock "><div class="pt-3 px-3 mb-3" ><div class="Card-list overflow-hidden horizontal-scrollable"><div class="itms-200  row row-cols-3  gy-3 gx-3"><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-kopshop tag-adidas card-type-supporterklubben card-author-postliverpool-no" data-category="supporterklubben"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/4hwbismw/lfc_kopshop_away_1_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc1cbfac2772f0&amp;cdv=638924930466870000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/4hwbismw/lfc_kopshop_away_1_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc1cbfac2772f0&amp;cdv=638924930466870000" title="lfc_kopshop_away_1_16x9.jpg" alt="lfc_kopshop_away_1_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Bortedrakten fra Adidas er nå på lager</h3><p class="card-text">Gjenforeningen mellom Liverpool FC og Adidas er et faktum. Hos KopShop finner du Liverpool-drakter, treningsklær og tilbehør.</p><a  class="read-more" href="https://www.kopshop.no/c/0/304/adidas" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit card-author-arve-vassbotten" data-category=""><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/iw2o3242/lfc_kopshop_eu-training-2_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc26e531ef39c0&amp;cdv=638936086741400000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/iw2o3242/lfc_kopshop_eu-training-2_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc26e531ef39c0&amp;cdv=638936086741400000" title="lfc_kopshop_eu-training-2_16x9.jpg" alt="lfc_kopshop_eu-training-2_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Liverpool-regnjakke og flere nyheter</h3><a  class="read-more" href="https://www.kopshop.no/c/0/304/adidas" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit card-author-kopshop" data-category=""><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/qsjfssq5/thumbnail_lfc_kopshop_1_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc0d4f11f9bff0&amp;cdv=638907954169430000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/qsjfssq5/thumbnail_lfc_kopshop_1_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc0d4f11f9bff0&amp;cdv=638907954169430000" title="Nye drakter" alt="Nye drakter" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Draktene i salg hos KopShop</h3><p class="card-text">Endelig er draktene tilbake i sortimentet – sammen med mange andre nyheter fra Adidas.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/8/draktene-salg-hos-1f/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-ryan_gravenberch tag-skader card-type-nyhet card-author-jens-bessesen" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/bisouova/gettyimages-2240224103_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c3b3fa642f0&amp;cdv=638959546082870000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/bisouova/gettyimages-2240224103_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c3b3fa642f0&amp;cdv=638959546082870000" title="GettyImages-2240224103_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2240224103_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><p>Gikk ut med mulig skade:</p><h3>&nbsp;– Føler meg bra</h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/gravenberch-ble-47/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 13.okt. 12:46</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-light-green has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-joe_gomez card-type-nyhet card-author-jens-bessesen" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/qozdgk4f/gettyimages-2238111481_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0.20371599203715993&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c5a8080f350&amp;cdv=638959680314930000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/qozdgk4f/gettyimages-2238111481_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0.20371599203715993&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c5a8080f350&amp;cdv=638959680314930000" title="GettyImages-2238111481_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2238111481_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3>Vil hente Gomez i januar</h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/ac-milan-ikke-gitt-1b/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 13.okt. 11:03</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Focus"><div class="bg-blue has-bg"><div class="image-crop-4x4 card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100 slimbg bg-inherit tag-the_kopite card-type-kopite card-author-arve-vassbotten" data-width=4 data-height=4 data-original=https://m.liverpool.no/images/tcrdf5d1/kopite-1_4x4.jpg?&amp;cc=0.22133483164104828,0,0.21615764337600835,0&amp;w=4&amp;h=4&amp;v=1dc230da571fc10><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3>Nå kan du lese nyeste Kopite digitalt</h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="https://www.liverpool.no/kopite/25/1/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Kopite</span><abbr>/ 11.sep. 11:13</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Complete"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="content-complete complete-stories"><div clas="complete-content-data"><div class="row"><div class="embededBlock "><div class="nocustomsettings" ><h2 class="section-heading pb-3">Nyhetene i kortform</h2>            <div class="Shorts-list horizontal-scrollable"><div class="ls-stories rss-reader rss-cards row g-3" data-url="/feed/stories/index.xml" data-view="card"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-NoImage"><div class="bg-light-yellow has-bg"><div class="card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100"><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Vil du oppleve Anfield denne sesongen? Her finner du pakketurer</h3><a  class="read-more" href="https://www.ving.no/fotballreiser/liverpool" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Reise</span><abbr>/ 16.sep. 11:27</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-mohamed_salah tag-landskamper card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/wl2ail0w/gettyimages-2236396552_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.3400241491684479,0.6150031807164354&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3bc774c572e0&amp;cdv=638959048757900000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/wl2ail0w/gettyimages-2236396552_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.3400241491684479,0.6150031807164354&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3bc774c572e0&amp;cdv=638959048757900000" title="Salahegypt" alt="Salahegypt" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Salah så lagkameratene fra tribunen</h3><p class="card-text">Mohamed Salah var ikke involvert da Egypt spilte foran egne supportere.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/salah-saa-5b/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 12.okt. 23:00</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-light-yellow has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit card-type-supporterklubben card-author-arve-vassbotten" data-category="supporterklubben"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/rqecgspy/tskjorter-og-bok_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc0a9c2fe64bb0&amp;cdv=638904986849070000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/rqecgspy/tskjorter-og-bok_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0,0,0,0&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc0a9c2fe64bb0&amp;cdv=638904986849070000" title="tskjorter og bok_16x9.jpg" alt="tskjorter og bok_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Få gullboka og t-skjorter tilsendt nå</h3><a  class="read-more" href="https://nettbutikk.liverpool.no/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Supporterklubben</span><abbr>/ 11.aug. 8:46</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Focus"><div class="bg-blue has-bg"><div class="image-crop-4x4 card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100 slimbg bg-inherit tag-alexander_isak tag-florian_wirtz tag-hugo_ekitike card-type-nyhet card-author-jens-bessesen" data-width=4 data-height=4 data-original=https://m.liverpool.no/images/bjddp4ps/gettyimages-2240310710_4x4.jpg?&amp;w=4&amp;h=4&amp;v=1dc3c1f4d71d230><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Må vinne for å holde liv i VM-drømmen</h3><p class="card-text">Stort press på Alexander Isak og Sverige mandag kveld. </p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/maa-vinne-holde-liv-4e/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 13.okt. 8:57</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-NoImage"><div class="bg-yellow has-bg"><div class="card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100"><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Medlemspris på Premier League-abonnement</h3><p class="card-text">Kommende sesong kan du se Premier League for kun kr 399,- per måned. Tilbudet er eksklusivt for våre medlemmer og varer ut hele 2025/26-sesongen.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/7/premier-league-til-28/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Supporterklubben</span><abbr>/ 1.jul. 10:29</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-white has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-liverpool_fc_women card-type-women card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="women"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/zn3lz1pn/gettyimages-2240598568_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.36202414782567455,0.6724534593680466&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3bbaa9e6bfe0&amp;cdv=638958993814700000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/zn3lz1pn/gettyimages-2240598568_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.36202414782567455,0.6724534593680466&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3bbaa9e6bfe0&amp;cdv=638958993814700000" title="Kapocs" alt="Kapocs" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Sjokkerte City, men det skulle ikke holde</h3><p class="card-text">Liverpool FC Women holdt ledelsen i 12 minutter mot topplaget.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/sjokkerte-city-men-21/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Women</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 21:00</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-white has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-tidligere_spillere tag-martin_kelly tag-legendekamp card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/iydbx2my/gettyimages-2239970763_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.36402414770360425,0.4560075108080739&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ba53a86d5f0&amp;cdv=638958901751830000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/iydbx2my/gettyimages-2239970763_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.36402414770360425,0.4560075108080739&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ba53a86d5f0&amp;cdv=638958901751830000" title="Kelly" alt="Kelly" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Fortalte om sin uvanlige kontrakt</h3><p class="card-text">Spillerforeningen PFA hadde ikke hørt om en lignende avtale som den Martin Kelly hadde i Liverpool FC.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/fortalte-uvanlige-37/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 18:25</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Complete"><div class="bg-light-green has-bg"><div class="content-complete complete-kommentar-og-innsikt"><div clas="complete-content-data"><div class="row"><div class="listBlock "><div class="pt-3 px-3 mb-3" ><div class="Card-list overflow-hidden horizontal-scrollable"><div class="has-category itms-200  row row-cols-3  gy-3 gx-3"><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-david_lynch tag-kommentar card-type-kommentar card-author-david-lynch" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2ozaaidr/17_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c6fda997a00&amp;cdv=638959772020800000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2ozaaidr/17_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3c6fda997a00&amp;cdv=638959772020800000" title="- (17)_16x9.png" alt="- (17)_16x9.png" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Nå kommer perioden som vil «avgjøre» sesongen</h3><p class="card-text">David Lynch skriver i ukens kommentar at Liverpools skrantende form kanskje har blitt skrevet og snakket litt for mye om.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/naa-kommer-perioden-3e/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-kommentar tag-arne_slot card-type-kommentar card-author-jens-bessesen" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/mg3kjc4h/sss_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc37da24733340&amp;cdv=638954730968200000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/mg3kjc4h/sss_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc37da24733340&amp;cdv=638954730968200000" title="sss_16x9.jpg" alt="sss_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Slapp av, folkens!</h3><p class="card-text">Tung oktober? Det har vært verre før. </p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/slapp-av-folkens-3d/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-david_lynch tag-mohamed_salah card-type-kommentar card-author-david-lynch" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/vnldum2t/gettyimages-2239334858_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.6100241326889567,0.4773905951724062&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc36cb1ab67b60&amp;cdv=638953566868700000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/vnldum2t/gettyimages-2239334858_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.6100241326889567,0.4773905951724062&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc36cb1ab67b60&amp;cdv=638953566868700000" title="Salahlynch" alt="Salahlynch" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Salah fortjener bedre – vi skylder ham tålmodighet</h3><p class="card-text">Fotballens lunefulle natur kommer tydelig til syne når mange av de samme Liverpool-supporterne som for bare noen måneder siden tryglet Mohamed Salah om å signere ny kontrakt, nå roper at han bør benkes.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/salah-fortjener-21/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-kommentar tag-arne_slot tag-chelsea tag-taktikk card-type-kommentar card-author-stefan-fosse" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/lncjxjdh/untitled-design-100_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3604ba21f930&amp;cdv=638952714844830000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/lncjxjdh/untitled-design-100_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3604ba21f930&amp;cdv=638952714844830000" title="Untitled design (100)_16x9.png" alt="Untitled design (100)_16x9.png" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Tre taktiske grep som bør skrotes før neste kamp</h3><p class="card-text">Arne Slot er utvilsomt en dyktig taktiker, men så langt denne sesongen har det blitt mer bom enn treff – senest mot Chelsea på Stamford Bridge.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/tegnebrettet-maa-33/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-florian_wirtz tag-tidligere_spillere tag-kommentar card-type-kommentar card-author-stefan-fosse" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/mahjfwqi/17-18-86_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc348db55ac490&amp;cdv=638951104151930000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/mahjfwqi/17-18-86_16x9.png?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc348db55ac490&amp;cdv=638951104151930000" title="17.  18 (86)_16x9.png (1)" alt="17.  18 (86)_16x9.png (1)" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Vi må ikke glemme alle «bomkjøpene» under Klopp</h3><p class="card-text">Florian Wirtz har ikke fått en perfekt Liverpool-start, men det gjaldt også flere nøkkelspillere i jakten på Champions League- og Premier League-triumfene.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/vi-maa-ikke-glemme-1a/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-kommentar tag-arne_slot tag-galatasaray card-type-kommentar card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/4oibxt13/gettyimages-2238395509_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3261212bb000&amp;cdv=638948713664000000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/4oibxt13/gettyimages-2238395509_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3261212bb000&amp;cdv=638948713664000000" title="GettyImages-2238395509_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2238395509_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Slot må ta tak før dette går skeis</h3><p class="card-text">To tap på rad skal ikke være nok til å krisemaksimere, men her må det tas grep – raskt.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/9/slot-maa-ta-tak-foer-5a/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-david_lynch tag-chelsea tag-manchester_city tag-arsenal tag-premier_league tag-kommentar card-type-kommentar card-author-david-lynch" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/r5oncvvc/gettyimages-2237750524_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc315791785350&amp;cdv=638947573086770000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/r5oncvvc/gettyimages-2237750524_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc315791785350&amp;cdv=638947573086770000" title="GettyImages-2237750524_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2237750524_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Det reises spørsmålstegn ved Liverpool, men hva med konkurrentene?</h3><p class="card-text">«En sikker oppskrift på å se dum ut når sesongen er over», skriver David Lynch i om dem som nå tviler på Liverpool.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/9/reises-42/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div><div class="col "><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100  bg-red has-bg tag-kommentar tag-crystal_palace card-type-kommentar card-author-jens-bessesen" data-category="kommentar"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/3rwnhad0/gettyimages-2237714300_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc30b2b6c94d30&amp;cdv=638946865043230000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/3rwnhad0/gettyimages-2237714300_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc30b2b6c94d30&amp;cdv=638946865043230000" title="GettyImages-2237714300_16x9.jpg" alt="GettyImages-2237714300_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Disse grepene burde Slot ta nå</h3><p class="card-text">Det får være måte på svartmaling for et lag som topper tabellen, men noen grep kan Arne Slot ta for å gjøre Liverpool litt bedre. </p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/9/disse-grepene-burde-42/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Focus"><div class="bg-blue has-bg"><div class="image-crop-4x4 card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100 slimbg bg-inherit tag-museum tag-museet card-type-kopite card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-width=4 data-height=4 data-original=https://m.liverpool.no/images/ibdccnoo/museum4_4x4.jpg?&amp;w=4&amp;h=4&amp;v=1dc37bbfcb90c30><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Den evige skattejakten i Liverpools historie </h3><p class="card-text">Liverpool FC har fått ny museumskurator. Det er en jobb som innebærer alt fra skattejakt til å fylle hullene i klubbens historie.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/evige-skattejakten-1f/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Kopite</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 8.okt. 12:11</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-white has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-florian_wirtz tag-j&#xFC;rgen_klopp tag-julian_nagelsmann card-type-innsikt card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="innsikt"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/3uah10zp/gettyimages-2240549367_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.5620241356186441,0.3783905981936463&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b8985cc7680&amp;cdv=638958782755600000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/3uah10zp/gettyimages-2240549367_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.5620241356186441,0.3783905981936463&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b8985cc7680&amp;cdv=638958782755600000" title="Wirtztyskland" alt="Wirtztyskland" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><p>Wirtz får stor støtte i hjemlandet</p><h3><strong>Klopp, landslagstreneren og flere profiler er sikre på at han vil bli en hit</strong></h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/fortsatt-full-tro-3b/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Innsikt</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 12.okt. 15:32</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-white has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-diogo_jota tag-ruben_neves card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2looojaa/gettyimages-2240472061_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4020311387233519,0.37035723387788094&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b74faf2bf10&amp;cdv=638958694526730000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2looojaa/gettyimages-2240472061_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4020311387233519,0.37035723387788094&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b74faf2bf10&amp;cdv=638958694526730000" title="Neves" alt="Neves" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Ble matchvinner med kompisens gamle nummer, pekte mot himmelen og viste frem denne tatoveringen</h3><p class="card-text">Ruben Neves var Diogo Jotas nærmeste venn. Da han scoret vinnermålet ett minutt på overtid var det tydelig hvor mye det betydde.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/ble-matchvinner-37/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 13:30</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-NoImage"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card bg-inherit overflow-hidden h-100"><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><p>LFC Women</p><h3><strong>Dette er laget som starter mot City</strong></h3><p></p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/dette-laget-starter-4f/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Women</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 16:51</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="bg-white has-bg"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-video tag-virgil_van_dijk card-has-embeded card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/u2bdmrqn/gettyimages-2240290944_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.1760129379485324,0.4455009085658805&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b65cb1bba80&amp;cdv=638958629299600000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/u2bdmrqn/gettyimages-2240290944_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.1760129379485324,0.4455009085658805&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b65cb1bba80&amp;cdv=638958629299600000" title="Virgilcody" alt="Virgilcody" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Se lagkameratene fra landslaget snakke om Virgil</h3><p class="card-text">Det er ti år siden Virgil van Dijk debuterte for Nederland.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/se-lagkameratene-fra-18/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 12:00</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-ibrahima_konate tag-skader tag-manchester_united card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/xlqhxw31/gettyimages-2227870668_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0.10539063040620027,0.020758731641496705,0.0088575185108297,0.23192692926462194&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc08478ca62070&amp;cdv=638902424309670000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/xlqhxw31/gettyimages-2227870668_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;cc=0.10539063040620027,0.020758731641496705,0.0088575185108297,0.23192692926462194&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc08478ca62070&amp;cdv=638902424309670000" title="Ibrahima Konate spillerprofil" alt="Ibrahima Konate spillerprofil" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Håper at Konaté kan bli klar til United-kampen</h3><p class="card-text">Ibrahima Konaté er sendt hjem fra landslagssamling, men Liverpool håper fortsatt at han kan spille mot Manchester United.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/haaper-at-konate-kan-44/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 11.okt. 15:42</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-liverpool_fc_women tag-sophie_roman_haug card-type-women card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="women"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2jfoidca/gettyimages-2239962657_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b64dbbbf950&amp;cdv=638958625283570000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2jfoidca/gettyimages-2239962657_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b64dbbbf950&amp;cdv=638958625283570000" title="Roman Haug" alt="Roman Haug" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Møter topplag på Anfield, i en kamp som vises på norsk TV</h3><p class="card-text">Liverpool FC Women skal i aksjon mot Manchester City denne søndagen.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/moeter-topplag-41/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Women</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 10:43</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-sean_dyche tag-nottingham_forest tag-ange_postecoglou tag-nuno_espirito_santo card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/kkjbmede/gettyimages-2239193938_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b57bb0988b0&amp;cdv=638958568900430000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/kkjbmede/gettyimages-2239193938_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3b57bb0988b0&amp;cdv=638958568900430000" title="Ange" alt="Ange" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Kan måtte møte Dyche heller enn Ange…</h3><p class="card-text">Det er vanskelig å se for seg to mer ulike spillestiler.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/kan-maatte-moete-20/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 12.okt. 9:11</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-nederland tag-landskamper tag-virgil_van_dijk tag-cody_gakpo tag-ryan_gravenberch tag-jeremie_frimpong tag-viteszlav_jaros tag-kostas_tsimikas card-type-liveblogg card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="liveblogg"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/eenf5zo0/gettyimages-2239211443_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.3500241485580964,0.4983906783667404&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc385c9f042d30&amp;cdv=638955291370270000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/eenf5zo0/gettyimages-2239211443_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.3500241485580964,0.4983906783667404&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc385c9f042d30&amp;cdv=638955291370270000" title="Virgil (2)" alt="Virgil (2)" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Flere røde i aksjon i dag</h3><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/flere-roede-aksjon-3c/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Liveblogg</span><abbr>/ 12.okt. 9:39</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-steven_gerrard tag-tidligere_spillere card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/qazlo2fq/gerrard_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dbe91baeac2e30&amp;cdv=638868151041470000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/qazlo2fq/gerrard_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dbe91baeac2e30&amp;cdv=638868151041470000" title="Gerrard" alt="Gerrard" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Gerrard blir likevel ikke Rangers-sjef</h3><p class="card-text">Fredag kveld ble det rapportert at en enighet var nær. Nå har han trukket seg.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/gerrard-blir-likevel-3f/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 11.okt. 21:31</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-conor_bradley tag-landskamper card-type-innsikt card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="innsikt"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/aidp4ine/gettyimages-2239784822_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4560241420883702,0.6529158104792524&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3aaf20d7be90&amp;cdv=638957844758970000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/aidp4ine/gettyimages-2239784822_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4560241420883702,0.6529158104792524&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3aaf20d7be90&amp;cdv=638957844758970000" title="Bradley" alt="Bradley" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">«Bradley var helt utrolig»</h3><p class="card-text">Conor Bradley var banens beste, men fikk et gult kort som gjør at han nå kan returnere tidlig til Merseyside.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/bradley-var-helt-56/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Innsikt</span><em class="me-1">/ Medlem</em><abbr>/ 11.okt. 17:58</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-12"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-ryan_babel tag-legendekamp tag-martin_skrtel card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2idhpb5u/gettyimages-2239970846_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.24202415514989287,0.6487653454609388&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ae08cbbb770&amp;cdv=638958057022470000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/2idhpb5u/gettyimages-2239970846_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.24202415514989287,0.6487653454609388&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ae08cbbb770&amp;cdv=638958057022470000" title="Babel (1)" alt="Babel (1)" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Babel ble matchvinner for legendene og feiret som Jota</h3><p class="card-text">Liverpool vant en kamp der det ble høy temperatur mellom Martin Skrtel og Diego Costa.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/babel-ble-56/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 11.okt. 18:57</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-skader tag-ibrahima_konate card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/ecgns0wx/gettyimages-2239213900_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4660241414780187,0.42273272019905167&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ab429dee4f0&amp;cdv=638957866385270000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/ecgns0wx/gettyimages-2239213900_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4660241414780187,0.42273272019905167&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ab429dee4f0&amp;cdv=638957866385270000" title="Konateskade" alt="Konateskade" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Skadet Konaté forlater landslagssamling</h3><p class="card-text">Ibrahima Konaté er sendt tilbake til Merseyside.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/konate-forlater-3e/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Nyhet</span><abbr>/ 11.okt. 13:38</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-legendekamp card-type-liveblogg card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="liveblogg"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/gbcbnvvz/gettyimages-2206417731_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4360241433090733,0.3995041399477691&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ac5e5433eb0&amp;cdv=638957942543630000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/gbcbnvvz/gettyimages-2206417731_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;rxy=0.4360241433090733,0.3995041399477691&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3ac5e5433eb0&amp;cdv=638957942543630000" title="babel" alt="babel" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Dette er legendelaget som starter på Stamford Bridge</h3><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/dette-legendelaget-49/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Liveblogg</span><abbr>/ 11.okt. 15:47</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-pausepraten tag-reise card-has-embeded card-type-pausepraten card-author-redaksjonen" data-category="pausepraten"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="https://m.liverpool.no/images/rbchmeny/nyberynnger-ss_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3a1740beb0d0&amp;cdv=638957192459170000" data-width="16" data-height="9" data-original="https://m.liverpool.no/images/rbchmeny/nyberynnger-ss_16x9.jpg?icr=16x9&amp;w=16&amp;h=9&amp;v=1dc3a1740beb0d0&amp;cdv=638957192459170000" title="nyberynnger ss_16x9.jpg" alt="nyberynnger ss_16x9.jpg" /></div></figure></div><div class="card-body overflow-hidden"><h3 class="card-title">Liverpoolreise for nybegynneren</h3><p class="card-text">Skal du på din første Liverpool-tur? Vi har noen tips til deg.</p><a  class="read-more" href="/lfc/25/a/liverpoolreise-23/" title="Les mer">Les mer</a></div><div class="card-footer overflow-hidden"><small><span class="me-1">Pausepraten</span><abbr>/ 11.okt. 12:12</abbr></small></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col  col-6"><div class="  content-type-Card"><div class="nocustomsettings"><div class="card overflow-hidden h-100 bg-inherit tag-pepe_reina tag-legendekamp tag-chelsea card-type-nyhet card-author-arild-skjaveland" data-category="nyhet"><div class="card-img-top"><figure class="figure d-block m-0"><div class="image-crop-16x9"><img class="figure-img image slimimage m-0" src="http